Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.49,0:00:15.70,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,What is happiness, I wonder?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.58,0:00:20.70,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Is it similar to youth?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.70,0:00:24.29,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,What is youth, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:44.56,0:00:46.23,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,"Something radiant."
Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.85,0:00:48.23,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Those were Kotori's words.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.27,0:00:50.48,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,"The hell should I know?"
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.48,0:00:52.19,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,"Waste of time thinking about it,"
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.19,0:00:53.24,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,Here they come.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.24,0:00:54.95,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,...said Yoshino, dismissively.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.24,0:00:58.37,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,Let's go, you bastards!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:00.74,0:01:02.37,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:05.00,0:01:05.96,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,A long time ago,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:07.29,0:01:11.13,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,someone said, "Life is like walking a tightrope."
Dialogue: 10,0:01:13.17,0:01:17.18,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,All three of their opinions seemed correct to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:18.34,0:01:19.68,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,It's something dazzling,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.68,0:01:21.18,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,mysterious,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.68,0:01:23.14,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,and terrifying.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:24.27,0:01:26.35,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Of course it's hard to answer.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:26.35,0:01:29.15,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Because there's no right answer to that question.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.23,0:01:34.36,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Regardless,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.36,0:01:38.87,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I decided to set out on a journey to look for it.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:40.41,0:01:41.37,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:42.20,0:01:43.12,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,All I wanted
Dialogue: 10,0:01:44.12,0:01:45.54,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,was to spend that thing
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.37,0:01:49.63,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,called "youth" with everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.01,0:02:02.26,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,That day, mankind heard it.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.41,0:02:21.16,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.16,0:02:25.66,Default,Drive,0,0,0,,Hey, what the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.77,0:02:54.11,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,The song of destruction
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.98,0:02:56.44,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,which signaled the world's demise.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.46,0:03:15.59,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,It's morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.59,0:03:17.26,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Rise and shine, sleepyhead.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.26,0:03:19.09,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,We've gotten separated from everyone,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.55,0:03:20.84,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,so I'm feeling lonely.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.44,0:03:31.81,Default,Giru,0,0,0,,What the heck is that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.90,0:03:43.49,Default,Pani,0,0,0,,That creature feels familiar.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.49,0:03:44.24,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.82,0:03:47.70,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,I suggest you not rely on your\Nrewrite ability so readily.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.70,0:03:50.66,Default,Saku,0,0,0,,Overuse it, and you will cease to be human.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.42,0:03:55.59,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Is that {\i1}you{\i0}?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.00,0:03:59.46,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.46,0:04:00.17,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Kagari.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.30,0:04:06.05,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Kagari...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.72,0:04:09.35,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Kotarou.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.35,0:04:11.68,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Is it time for my morning feecof?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.69,0:04:15.98,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.98,0:04:19.07,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,I don't hear that hair-raising song anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.90,0:04:20.69,Default,Giru,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.69,0:04:23.70,Default,Giru,0,0,0,,The song of destruction stopped at some point!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.70,0:04:28.45,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Kagari!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.83,0:04:30.08,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.08,0:04:31.25,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Seriously!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.95,0:04:35.37,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I honestly thought I'd never get to see you again.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.96,0:04:37.46,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Kotarou?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.17,0:04:40.21,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,Is that the Key?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.26,0:04:43.47,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Esaka-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.22,0:04:49.35,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,You don't seem particularly surprised.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.76,0:04:51.85,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Something told me you would show up.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.90,0:04:59.32,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,Then I trust you are aware of what I'm after.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.32,0:05:02.86,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,I will put an end to the Key, here and now.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.86,0:05:04.20,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I won't let you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.20,0:05:05.45,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Kotarou-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.03,0:05:09.45,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,I never expected you to have an ability like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.45,0:05:15.83,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}This guy is strong!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.88,0:05:25.09,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll never land a hit unless\NI shift up one—no, {\i0}ten{\i1} gears.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.64,0:05:28.76,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.89,0:05:34.81,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.14,0:05:37.85,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,A lesser-skilled opponent would surely look...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.85,0:05:40.11,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,for a surprise attack to my blind spot.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.61,0:05:43.57,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,But no matter how fast that attack may be,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.57,0:05:46.36,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,it poses no trouble when I'm anticipating it.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.11,0:05:48.32,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was naïve!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.32,0:05:50.99,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I step it up ten gears, he's still way beyond me!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.99,0:05:51.62,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}In that case!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.62,0:05:53.37,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Don't, Kotarou-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.37,0:05:56.37,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I just have to keep stepping it up until I reach him!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.50,0:06:00.50,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.17,0:06:03.25,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Kotarou...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.56,0:06:14.10,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Sakuya...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.70,0:06:32.24,Default,Gen,0,0,0,,Sorry, Captain.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.83,0:06:36.00,Default,Gen,0,0,0,,This is the end of the line for the\NBayern Knights of the Green Sword...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.54,0:06:38.87,Default,Gen,0,0,0,,Hit, and you'll be hit back.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.87,0:06:40.88,Default,Gen,0,0,0,,That goes for Gaia and Guardian alike.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.88,0:06:43.54,Default,Gen,0,0,0,,And when it's over something\Nimportant, that goes double.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.13,0:06:48.01,Default,Gen,0,0,0,,Bloody hell. Talk about a sinful life.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.01,0:06:50.89,Default,Gen,0,0,0,,If there {\i1}is{\i0} a world after this one, then...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.97,0:06:54.76,Default,Gen,0,0,0,,As long as I can make delicious ramen,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.76,0:06:56.43,Default,Gen,0,0,0,,that'll be plenty enough for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.15,0:07:05.02,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,Your attacks lack variety!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.02,0:07:06.53,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Damn it, again!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.94,0:07:10.03,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,They're powerful, but little else.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.03,0:07:12.87,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,Don't expect a heavy swing like that\nto connect more than once!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.95,0:07:17.62,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,Attacks should be simple,\Nbut with force behind them.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.04,0:07:19.16,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Kotarou-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.42,0:07:28.42,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.42,0:07:29.55,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Just a little more!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.17,0:07:32.30,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,The bleeding stopped?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.64,0:07:33.89,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,That power...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.89,0:07:34.80,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.14,0:07:37.56,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,Your body appears to have remembered.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.56,0:07:39.31,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.31,0:07:42.23,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,That's irrelevant to you as you are now.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.81,0:07:45.06,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,Furthermore,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.06,0:07:48.32,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,I cannot stand to see you\Nin that sorry state any longer.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.82,0:07:51.15,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,Tennouji...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.70,0:07:55.83,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,If only you hadn't come back\Nin such a half-baked condition...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.83,0:07:58.33,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,What the hell are you going on about?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.08,0:08:06.46,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,M-My body—
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.00,0:08:09.71,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,The only mercy I can offer you\Nis to end this in one swing.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.26,0:08:12.22,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,This is farewell.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.22,0:08:12.84,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Kota—
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.84,0:08:13.34,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Sto—
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.43,0:08:16.93,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Kotarou!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.93,0:08:17.43,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.27,0:08:20.27,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shizuru!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.27,0:08:21.60,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kotarou.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.24,0:08:35.66,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,How utterly reckless.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.66,0:08:36.45,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Gramps...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.41,0:08:38.83,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,You won't regret this?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.83,0:08:39.70,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I won't!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.83,0:08:42.96,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.66,0:08:45.33,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,Then the time for words has passed.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.88,0:08:46.79,Default,Esa,0,0,0,,En garde!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.47,0:08:59.85,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Kotarou...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.85,0:09:00.72,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Kagari!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.18,0:09:05.31,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Guess I went up too many gears.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.31,0:09:06.15,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Crap.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.15,0:09:08.11,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,My body feels like it's going to rip apart!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.61,0:09:10.61,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Kotarou-kun, are you all ri—
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.40,0:09:18.16,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Looks like the tab I've racked\Nup is due for payment.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.83,0:09:22.37,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I'm like a daemon, aren't I?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.21,0:09:25.37,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.37,0:09:26.42,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.42,0:09:27.25,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Kotori?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.75,0:09:32.76,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,I did this to you...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.76,0:09:36.13,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.13,0:09:39.76,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,I now understand why I was drawn to Kotarou.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.51,0:09:43.18,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,I am inside him.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.18,0:09:45.77,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,This was your doing, wasn't it, Kotori?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.85,0:09:52.27,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,The day the Key appeared from the power spot,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.27,0:09:55.57,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,I came to the forest for you,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.57,0:09:57.66,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,in order to fulfill my promise as a druid.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.24,0:10:05.04,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,For some reason, Kotarou-kun was there, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.79,0:10:08.62,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kotarou-kun! Kotarou-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.37,0:10:08.62,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,And he was at death's door.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.96,0:10:12.42,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,All I wanted was to save him,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.29,0:10:14.13,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{\an8}Please, save Kotarou-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.42,0:10:15.13,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,so I begged you over and over.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.13,0:10:16.92,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.22,0:10:24.18,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,I embedded your ribbon inside\NKotarou-kun's right arm,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.18,0:10:27.69,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,and managed to save his life.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.02,0:10:30.77,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,I wanted him to live.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.48,0:10:33.82,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,I didn't want him to disappear \Nsomewhere far away,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.82,0:10:36.61,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,like Mom and Dad.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.61,0:10:40.91,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,But that just ended up making him suffer more!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.62,0:10:46.20,Default,Giru,0,0,0,,H-Hey! Hang in there!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.20,0:10:47.04,Default,Pani,0,0,0,,It is all right.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.04,0:10:49.33,Default,Pani,0,0,0,,He has simply lost consciousness.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.33,0:10:53.17,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,My power is too much for humans to handle.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.17,0:10:58.17,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,While it amplified Kotarou's powers,\Nit also placed a terrible burden upon him.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.17,0:10:59.63,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Then, what should we do?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.63,0:11:03.39,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,You could remove my power and return it to me...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.39,0:11:06.72,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,But then, what will happen to him?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.72,0:11:08.98,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Your power is what closed his wounds,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.98,0:11:11.27,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,and is keeping him alive.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.27,0:11:12.73,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,I do not know,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.73,0:11:14.77,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,but at this rate,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.77,0:11:16.78,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,he will definitely lose his life.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.49,0:11:21.49,Default,Giru,0,0,0,,Aw, guess we ain't got no choice then!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.49,0:11:22.53,Default,Pani,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.28,0:11:29.16,Default,Pani,0,0,0,,Put simply, a huge hole will open\Nup in Kotarou-san, correct?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.16,0:11:30.04,Default,Pani,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.04,0:11:30.66,Default,Giru,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.66,0:11:34.79,Default,Giru,0,0,0,,For a big guy like me,\Nain't a hole that can't be plugged up!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.79,0:11:35.67,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.67,0:11:37.42,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Do you realize what you're saying?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.42,0:11:41.09,Default,Giru,0,0,0,,It just happened to work out that way,\Nbut we {\i1}did{\i0} form a contract.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.09,0:11:43.30,Default,Pani,0,0,0,,We have to make ourselves useful once in a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.89,0:11:46.14,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.66,0:12:03.53,Default,Giru,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.53,0:12:06.49,Default,Pani,0,0,0,,Though it was only for a short time, it was fun!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.71,0:12:14.33,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Kotarou-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.83,0:12:15.88,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Kotori.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.34,0:12:20.21,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Want some morning feecof?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.63,0:12:21.67,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Sounds nice.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.67,0:12:22.63,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Of course,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.63,0:12:25.84,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,we don't have any beans, hot water, sugar, or milk.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.84,0:12:30.68,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,But you're walking around\Nwith cups in this situation?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.23,0:12:35.06,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Don't push yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.06,0:12:38.61,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,You're just barely alive right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.86,0:12:42.61,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Gil and Pani aren't here, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.86,0:12:46.53,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Those two ran away.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.03,0:12:49.79,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,They said they couldn't deal \Nwith us, and went far away...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.66,0:12:51.66,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.66,0:12:53.54,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Well, knowing them,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.54,0:12:55.37,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,they'll be fine wherever they go.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.63,0:13:00.13,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,What's happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.13,0:13:03.92,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Nothing much has changed\Nsince that song stopped.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.13,0:13:06.34,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.14,0:13:10.64,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Well, I guess {\i1}I{\i0} changed a little.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.64,0:13:12.14,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,How so?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.14,0:13:16.81,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,You have not evolved from the same foolish, rash,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.81,0:13:19.15,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,blockheaded human you always were.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.15,0:13:21.15,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Hey, you don't have to force yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.99,0:13:26.66,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Kagari!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.28,0:13:29.24,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Kotarou-kun, this is...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.24,0:13:30.28,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.28,0:13:32.66,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Damn it, I hear it!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.66,0:13:34.83,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,The song of destruction!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.92,0:13:46.80,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Kotarou-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.18,0:13:53.14,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.14,0:13:55.06,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,He doesn't have Kagari's power anymore!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.31,0:14:00.52,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,Survival is utterly without meaning.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.52,0:14:03.57,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,This land is filled with naught but sorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.57,0:14:06.57,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,That being so, life is unnecessary to this world!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.07,0:14:10.82,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,Let this song resound!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.78,0:14:15.41,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,Destruction is the one and only Salvation
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.41,0:14:18.12,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,you foolish lifeforms shall be granted!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.46,0:14:23.09,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,The pump has been sufficiently primed.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.55,0:14:25.30,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,Everything is in order.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.30,0:14:26.42,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,Now, Key!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.88,0:14:30.30,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,Grant these sinful lives Salvation!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.43,0:14:35.47,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Kagari!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.68,0:14:38.06,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Kagari!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.38,0:15:03.54,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Kagari!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.43,0:15:11.47,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Kagari!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.80,0:15:14.22,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Kotarou-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.52,0:15:22.10,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Kagari! Kagari!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.24,0:15:30.74,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Let me go, damn it!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.24,0:15:34.12,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I still need to talk to her!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.12,0:15:36.20,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Kagari!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.00,0:15:47.50,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,No! Not the face!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.01,0:15:51.30,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,What will I do with you, Kotarou?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.63,0:15:54.97,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,You're always so mean to me...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.89,0:15:59.64,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,You must be super-duper totally in love with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.52,0:16:01.81,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.86,0:16:11.20,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,This is the Salvation?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.40,0:16:16.41,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,The world is going to end, due to my ruling?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.41,0:16:17.53,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.53,0:16:20.37,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,The other Kagari is the one\Nwho made the final ruling.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.04,0:16:23.33,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,No, it was me.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.50,0:16:27.46,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I'm sure there must still be some other way.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.46,0:16:29.59,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,The feecof was delicious.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.59,0:16:30.42,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.84,0:16:33.80,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,The internet and school were both fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.80,0:16:37.05,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Kotori and the others were\Nnoteworthy humans, as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.05,0:16:38.81,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,What are you...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.81,0:16:42.02,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,And, most of all, the days I spent with you
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.02,0:16:45.85,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,were the finest, most irreplaceable memories.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.81,0:16:47.69,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Kagari?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.69,0:16:49.32,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Will you...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.11,0:16:51.69,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,save this world?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.45,0:16:55.45,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Do you know what you're saying?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.45,0:16:56.95,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.95,0:17:00.20,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind dying if it was at your hands.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.21,0:17:12.46,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Kotarou-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.17,0:17:14.59,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.80,0:17:20.72,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,You think I could actually bring myself to do that?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.72,0:17:23.68,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.68,0:17:26.48,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I... care too much about...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.36,0:17:34.07,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,Kotarou, among all the humans in this world,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.07,0:17:37.78,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,you truly are the most\Nhelplessly foolish of them all.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.37,0:17:46.79,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.27,0:18:06.02,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.52,0:18:12.69,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.69,0:18:14.90,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Let's have some saury.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.44,0:18:17.03,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Dad,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.65,0:18:19.49,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Mom,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.49,0:18:22.53,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,and Shizuka...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.29,0:18:25.54,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Let's all eat, together.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.08,0:18:27.54,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.54,0:18:30.04,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Let's do that tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.04,0:18:34.30,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,We aren't alone anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.76,0:18:36.05,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,We...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.47,0:18:39.30,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,We have everyone...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.19,0:18:52.06,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,They're disappearing!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.06,0:18:53.65,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,The world!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.65,0:18:55.32,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,Humans!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.32,0:18:57.90,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,And us!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.16,0:19:06.08,Default,Shima,0,0,0,,Akane...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.30,0:19:16.84,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,Shimako...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.52,0:19:30.10,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Sakuya?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.48,0:19:33.15,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,I'll pick you up now.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.82,0:19:38.40,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,I never knew.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.40,0:19:42.03,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,You were this heavy, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.41,0:19:43.66,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,From now on,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.95,0:19:47.04,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,I'll be the one carrying you...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.96,0:19:55.21,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,It was never easy,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.92,0:20:00.26,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,but we did everything we could, huh, Chibi-Moth?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.80,0:20:05.10,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Little one?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.97,0:20:09.56,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Pero?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.81,0:20:12.81,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Is that you, Pero?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.74,0:20:22.90,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,You were with me all this time!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.20,0:20:27.45,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,I wonder if we'll get to see everyone again?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.66,0:20:31.20,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,That sure would be wonderful...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.45,0:21:12.25,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Everyone is ascending.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.25,0:21:15.71,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Gaia, Guardian, the Key.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.71,0:21:17.42,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I was involved with them all,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.38,0:21:20.46,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,but I couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.09,0:21:24.38,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,If I had a little more time,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.38,0:21:26.76,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I wonder if I could have done everything better?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.76,0:21:28.30,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.30,0:21:30.85,Default,Kaga,0,0,0,,I'm sure you could, Kotarou.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.64,0:21:33.64,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:08.63,0:24:09.92,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\an8}I have to rewrite it all.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:10.59,0:24:13.72,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'll do things better next time.
Comment: 0,0:24:15.64,0:24:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 3,0:22:03.42,0:22:07.17,ED2-R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}owariyuku jidai ni mo
Dialogue: 3,0:22:07.17,0:22:13.43,ED2-R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}tashika ni mebuku inochi ga aru no, hora
Dialogue: 3,0:22:14.30,0:22:18.11,ED2-R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}hitomi wo tojita nara
Dialogue: 3,0:22:18.11,0:22:23.94,ED2-R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}ima wa sono kodou ga yasashii
Dialogue: 3,0:22:25.23,0:22:29.36,ED2-R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}nureta hoho wo naderu
Dialogue: 3,0:22:29.78,0:22:35.33,ED2-R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}kaze ni yureru kusa no you ni
Dialogue: 3,0:22:35.33,0:22:45.13,ED2-R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}kimi to futari yorisoi mitodokete yuketara ii ne
Dialogue: 3,0:22:46.75,0:22:50.80,ED2-R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}kurayami ni kakuretemo
Dialogue: 3,0:22:50.80,0:22:53.55,ED2-R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}hana no kaori mo
Dialogue: 3,0:22:53.55,0:22:57.97,ED2-R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}mushi no haoto mo soko ni aru no
Dialogue: 3,0:22:57.97,0:23:01.73,ED2-R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}wakariaeta no nara
Dialogue: 3,0:23:01.73,0:23:09.19,ED2-R,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}kanjitoretara te wo tsunagou
Dialogue: 2,0:22:03.42,0:22:07.17,ED2-E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}Even as the end draws near
Dialogue: 2,0:22:07.17,0:22:13.43,ED2-E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}There's budding life still here, see?
Dialogue: 2,0:22:14.30,0:22:18.11,ED2-E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}If you close your eyes
Dialogue: 2,0:22:18.11,0:22:23.94,ED2-E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}You'll feel the gentle heartbeat
Dialogue: 2,0:22:25.23,0:22:29.36,ED2-E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}That gently caresses your damp cheeks
Dialogue: 2,0:22:29.78,0:22:35.33,ED2-E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}Like a wind that makes the grass sway
Dialogue: 2,0:22:35.33,0:22:45.13,ED2-E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}I wish I could see the end by your side
Dialogue: 2,0:22:46.75,0:22:50.80,ED2-E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}Though hidden in the darkness
Dialogue: 2,0:22:50.80,0:22:53.55,ED2-E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}The scent of the flowers
Dialogue: 2,0:22:53.55,0:22:57.97,ED2-E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}And the buzzing of insects are there
Dialogue: 2,0:22:57.97,0:23:01.73,ED2-E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}If you understand
Dialogue: 2,0:23:01.73,0:23:09.19,ED2-E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}If you can feel them, let's hold hands
