Dialogue: 2,0:00:18.20,0:00:24.50,Hand2,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(35,14)\fs36\c&H747B80&\blur0.5\fad(0,150)}Consequently, Gaia devised the Song of\N Destruction's ceremony to bring about the Salvation.\N\NTennouji, if you want to ward off our destruction,\N kill the Key. \N\NYou may be able to do it, given how unguarded it \Nis with you.\N\NThink hard and decide whether you will secure \Nthis planet's future, or mankind's present.
